<emphasis id="EBC9EAE76B54BB77FF28C7DF01B7FA49" bold="true" box="[136,253,1449,1471]" pageId="3">FIGURE 3.</emphasis>
Geographical location of the 
<taxonomicName id="1EBD4D766B54BB77FDBAC7DC038AFA49" authorityName="Z. Acosta" authorityYear="2022" box="[538,704,1449,1471]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Myrtaceae" genus="Myrcia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="3" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="urquiolae">
<emphasis id="EBC9EAE76B54BB77FDBAC7DC038AFA49" box="[538,704,1449,1471]" italics="true" pageId="3">Myrcia urquiolae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
population in Holguín (eastern Cuba), La Mensura-Piloto National Park, near the Naranjo river, in the charrascales of La Caridad.
</paragraph>
